{"tid":377570,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得做雞本身無錯","createTime":"2017-08-27T19:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T19:11:42.000Z","uid":42625,"like":86,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"159fb1d9eb6b23b0b495cab912561bb742a7eadc","tid":377570,"uid":42625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:00:35.000Z","msg":"今日同老母講起雞嘅話題，佢話：「唔好講埋啲咁核突嘅嘢啦，好唔道德囉。」<br />\n<br />\n我同佢講：「做雞出賣身體，我地打工出賣勞力，何罪之有呢？你知唔知無雞嘅話性罪行會多幾多，好有存在價值架。」<br />\n<br />\n老母答我：「之但係我覺得佢地出嚟做好危險囉，會俾變態佬殺架。」<br />\n<br />\n「我地講緊道德問題你講乜嘢危險唔危險？偷換概念都唔係咁用掛。」<br />\n<br />\n老母：「唔知呀，總之好核突啦佢地！好衰囉！」<br />\n<br />\n「核突係邊方面先？同好多人做過？咁你可以覺得佢地唔純潔，但佢地無害過人喎，你話一部分雞破壞家庭介入人地婚姻咁就叫害人啫（但無可避免會有呢種事發生），做雞本身有無害到人呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「總之佢地就係衰啦，唔講啦！」<br />\n<br />\n總結加感想<br />\n1. 我老母唔係好識咩係理性討論<br />\n2. 我覺得人人都講嘅嘢都唔一定係啱<br />\n3. 雞承受嘅風險同社會壓力好大，佢地嘅人生難捱好多<br />\n4. 啲雞本身係咪好人不在此論，我想講做雞嘅本質唔係道德問題<br />\n<br />\n如果係雛妓、扯皮條、逼人賣淫呢啲一定係錯，我指係一個成熟嘅人自願去做雞道德上唔係錯。<br />\n<br />\nPS. 唔係叫你去做雞或者援交PTGF嗰啲<br />\n再PS. 多數嘅援交妹太細個，唔識後果，<span style=\"color: red;\">年輕嘅你地唔該唔好做PTGF，你會親手破壞自己人生</span>，身體心靈價值觀都會被摧毀<br />\n<br />\n可能有其他方面我無考慮到，其實我想知做雞喺道德上係有咩問題？大家理性討論下"},{"pid":"faaccad68da2f9e6157b13637094bfd736c2dca4","tid":377570,"uid":89134,"like":9,"dislike":34,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:04:24.000Z","msg":"問題嚟啦 你同你老母講嘢<br />\n關我撚事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafe4f2a28d1776ced60c68e1a4b3e0f7e9b25de","tid":377570,"uid":42374,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:05:10.000Z","msg":"唔講啦！又提起返我啲傷心事！啊仔做咩你係要迫我講啫！"},{"pid":"b6be855ad368236800e16e0143e97e5e141ad51b","tid":377570,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:20:28.000Z","msg":"傳播性病係唔道德"},{"pid":"60d11191f8710cd03d9d8c67d2321e850c837445","tid":377570,"uid":42625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講啦！又提起返我啲傷心事！啊仔做咩你係要迫我講啫！</blockquote><br />\n笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913f0a3769a2ad5a44622cda548e6e1b65adb432","tid":377570,"uid":42625,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傳播性病係唔道德</blockquote><br />\n做雞呢個工作本質上唔包括傳播性病，而傳播性病係不安全性行為下嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n傳播性病本身係咪道德問題，我估係睇佢知唔知自己有傳染人，當然如果佢有心傳播性病係佢仆街"},{"pid":"d0ea90b5f0021086a335dc931bd2ab1f75d28aac","tid":377570,"uid":137669,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:31:31.000Z","msg":"同女人講道理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ae8bc896c05132cb467d3399806ae89df694bb","tid":377570,"uid":118351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:02:25.000Z","msg":"完全唔明做雞有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a451c47bc9c279fd4b310b8ccf6c05ae3cd303","tid":377570,"uid":56498,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:39:29.000Z","msg":"即刻駁咀！"},{"pid":"359a06b2ac508d08eb76d56155b69b874d3db6f1","tid":377570,"uid":128127,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:49:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得如果用自己身體黎賺錢養家冇問題<br />\n相反成日背住自己條女叫雞果啲仆街最錯"},{"pid":"243dad16adbc50923053ff1d68715c2129601e00","tid":377570,"uid":90704,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:11:13.000Z","msg":"樓主要討論就討論幫雞奶閪有乜問題<br />\n我相信大把雞蟲認為冇問題<br />\n佢地會話啲雞出黎搵食注重衞生<br />\n你條女都冇咁乾淨<br />\n我持相反意見比佢地話我唔理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439da47e29dc38b1fc6ae5c692dfd50cb1f68155","tid":377570,"uid":53682,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:20:00.000Z","msg":"理論上：當係工具 物化女性 <br />\n但自己諗吓實際上係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常都係啲人「性潔癖」"},{"pid":"38f4bc3b8a3789039981be170348dc3178aa490a","tid":377570,"uid":7789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔講啦！又提起返我啲傷心事！啊仔做咩你係要迫我講啫！</blockquote><br />\n笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6137d8180762d31a10b2ae742ad35692a1d72328","tid":377570,"uid":54927,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:28:14.000Z","msg":"你同你老母講道理懶係型本身已經係on9既行為"},{"pid":"bfd1ce2f3cb3a2bc3af813bd7eaacc97cbdab26e","tid":377570,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:31:50.000Z","msg":"一講「總之」已經係盲目 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f0e35a527e795c606f60ceb66a1b0fcc7fddea","tid":377570,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:38:08.000Z","msg":"做雞本身無錯<br />\n祇要不是我家後院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e743643fa82267d7612105ece03c838424fcecd","tid":377570,"uid":98549,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:50:29.000Z","msg":"算把啦 大部份老一輩既人係唔聽人講野<br />\n同佢地理性討論跟本哂氣<br />\n佢地跟本唔客觀<br />\n 永遠堅守自己原本以為既立場 <br />\n佢地跟本唔會代入人地個角色黎諗野<br />\n只會由自己角度出發<br />\n<br />\n利申 我個名 <br />\n多年嘗試同阿媽理性溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc07a6e891f328f9d9dfecf60f896deed0afcb6","tid":377570,"uid":117237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:53:28.000Z","msg":"因為討論道德係唔道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47724e23bd18f330c85efabf47e26fc6eb0ec25","tid":377570,"uid":19151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同你老母講道理懶係型本身已經係on9既行為</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話"},{"pid":"8272211ef04f55ff8c5487e4a6e215829ddcd805","tid":377570,"uid":101367,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:25:22.000Z","msg":"之前新聞講啲人為咗幾千蚊運毒 我老母就話如果等錢洗做援交仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老母唔知我係臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a056403c4f9322a84cdbfeb5afcc879f7d82920","tid":377570,"uid":71389,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:40:15.000Z","msg":"既然係咁<br />\n樓主又接唔接到你條女/老婆出嚟做雞呢?<br />\n<br />\n你都話咗做雞道德上無問題<br />\n咁即係係一份正當職業<br />\n而你條女/老婆出嚟做雞都係打份工啫<br />\n咁樓主應該接受到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4aee289417c3b2fcc8c6d48492121ae6332a95b","tid":377570,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:42:41.000Z","msg":"同女人講邏輯道理已經錯左"},{"pid":"972f1e9fde021960600ef3b44d3e420b3b6a27fe","tid":377570,"uid":125365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算把啦 大部份老一輩既人係唔聽人講野<br />\n同佢地理性討論跟本哂氣<br />\n佢地跟本唔客觀<br />\n 永遠堅守自己原本以為既立場 <br />\n佢地跟本唔會代入人地個角色黎諗野<br />\n只會由自己角度出發<br />\n<br />\n利申 我個名 <br />\n多年嘗試同阿媽理性溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁樣諗其實都係無「代入人地個角色黎諗野」<br />\n<br />\n其實理性從來都可以話係／容易跌入一種精英主義，都係多思考啦"},{"pid":"62a7b6e741d978bd3c33efc3589314296e07005a","tid":377570,"uid":125365,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T22:53:25.000Z","msg":"佢既standpoint係based on 好多stereotyping（如果唔係佢可以有選擇去接受好d既教育底下應該某程度係可以justify，當然唔係話佢係岩，只係可被理解），而呢d定型都係inherit from歷史，which 可以追朔至最早期既社會<br />\n<br />\n狹義咁講女性地位同性自主，例如人類最早部落時期係母系社會，點解後尾會轉左父系，性別不平等同生產工具既關係等等"},{"pid":"66e824fd71ab32f9843a8b3d3a7965c65288256b","tid":377570,"uid":100760,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:38:38.000Z","msg":"小學雞先會同阿媽理論，稍為成熟啲都知理論嚟無謂"}]}